	(text "SEC 1  INPUT: isothermal Cu block. K5=mode: direct (high-Z) / SSR bridge (low-Z). SSR chop U4-U11 (2x parallel AQY221N2M per leg) to 100Hz - no contact EMF, no wear. K3=short/blank. K4=100k cal."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30 25 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "5ffef06c-0399-4d86-b53d-027f63f70d30")
	)
	(text "SEC 2  LSK389B x8 (4 duals): Q1-Q4 gate A, Q5-Q8 gate B. Id=2.5mA each (I_DSS>=6mA margin), tail 20mA. Cascode VB=2.77V -> VDS~1.7V. Loads 750R + 5mA bleed."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30 108 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "cd6050ad-12c3-4822-92d4-e2c93b6bfc45")
	)
	(text "SEC 3  OPA828 integrator + OPA2210A buffer in loop (designed 1-pole loop: fc 200kHz @G21 / 20kHz @G201, zero 480kHz). RN1 = SMNZ 4x1k: 1+2 = G201 top, 3+4 = G21 top. Bottoms: 10x100R par = 10R (G201), 100R (G21)."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30 208 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "23ad21ee-7ad6-4171-9ebf-b3e0c8e2ae51")
	)
	(text "SEC 4  BIPOLAR bias servo (leakage flows INTO gate node): DAC chA -> U2B x-2 inverter -> 10G sinks 0..-1nA; DAC chB -> 10G sources 0..+500pA. Filters fc=0.16Hz."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30 288 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "136c281f-0992-4406-af6a-e6cb966bb402")
	)
	(text "SEC 5  POWER: cap multipliers on both rails. J3 (20-pin) to isolators/drivers on dig board - now incl ADC SPI. SEC 6 (y300): LTC2500-32 + LTC6655 + LP5907 on-board, VOUT never leaves the PCB."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30 345 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "3e1556a0-c12d-4599-88e2-75decfd81e90")
	)
	(text "NOTES: (1) K3/K4/K5 wired per Panasonic ASCTB14E p.12 (VERIFIED): set coil 10(+)/6(-), reset coil 1(+)/5(-); COM 3/8, reset closes 2+9, set closes 4+7. (2b) MEASURE AQY221N2M off-leakage at 10mV, 25-45C, before committing."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 250 25 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "ae3f5e77-6ade-4741-aab8-25fe17ca8daf")
	)
	(text "(2) LSK389B: bin V_GS @5mA to <5mV; Cu thermal clamp over all 4 cans. IF3602 (InterFET direct) drops en 0.6->0.3nV/rtHz if sourced."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 250 30 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "f438dbf0-cb1a-4c66-8f19-bb5b79973837")
	)
	(text "(3) Signal path HI_IN..GATE_A all-Cu, crimped; no Sn joints inside isothermal block. Guard = STAR, single point."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 250 35 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "f90d7516-90b1-457d-852b-dd4ee3eb8fbf")
	)
	(text "(4) 10G resistor: PCB guard ring at BIAS_F potential; clean w/ IPA, no flux residue."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 250 40 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "59f26ed9-6128-45a1-84b2-f154678aaec4")
	)
